What should I do if I encounter issues with forking, network problems, or having an old version of the wallet?

If you encounter issues with forking, network problems, or having an old version of the wallet, you should refer to the Verus wiki's FAQ section, specifically the article on "Recover from forking, network or old wallet problems". This article provides guidance on how to resolve these issues.

If the problem persists, continue with this WIKI: [Recover from forking, network or old wallet problems](https://wiki.verus.io/#!faq-allos/faq-allos19_what_should_i_do_if_i_end_up_on_my_own_fork_because_of_a_network_issue_or_having_an_old_version_of_the_wallet.md)
